    </author>
    <date day="25" month="January" year="2013"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo specifies a TPMKEY Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) Scheme
   for identifying cryptographic keys stored in TPM chips and accessed
   using the TCG Software Stack (TSS).  The URI is based on how TPM keys
   are identified in the TSS specification.</t>
    </abstract>
